acceptance_criteria: "Checked-in budget manifest (bytes + approx tokens) for a representative invocation corpus: pm --help, per-noun help, contracts summary/full, list/get/context/next/search in default+json+toon, MCP tool-list payload; deterministic fixture workspace; gate wired into the CI static-gates job; failure output names the offending command and the delta; budgets change only via an explicit reviewed commit (eslint-suppressions baseline pattern); budget-update procedure documented"
